Ruination
[[Image:Ruinationipa.jpg|thumb|Ruination now comes in a clearly-labeled, convenient liquid form.]]
Ruination has nothing to do with the shitty deathcore band Job For A Cowboy. Ruination comes from the term "I am going to ruin your [[Internets]]!!!" Ruination encompasses many different types of abuse, hacking, harassment and general annoyances directed at another, or in some cases, one's self. This is referred to as "self-ruination". Ruination is also a euphemism for [[anal sex]]. 

