== Self-Ruination ==
Self-ruination is a process of ruining one's own life through various methods. Typically these methods can only be participated in by the object and no other person can initiate or stop these acts. Self-ruination typically consists of anything that is generally regarded as a very bad decision; such as excessive drug use, alcohol consumption or lifestyle habits. Self-ruination can also be inflicted through over-obsession with a significant other or by financial ruination wherein the subject does not earn enough money to compensate for their habits. [[Gek]] is the best example of self-ruination in modern times, while [[Hitler]] is an excellent theoretical example. Another contemporary self-ruiner is [[Snitch]] who has demonstrated great capacity to fuck his own shit up. Self-urination and self-ruination are closely related to each other.

